    <item>
      <title>在达成协议之前，特朗普要求伊朗投降。他有一个惊喜。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/trump-iran-deal-nuclear-program-strait.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管伊朗人在战争中遭受了巨大损失，但他们在与世界上最强大的军队的对抗中脱颖而出，证明了他们可以利用经济混乱作为武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/trump-iran-deal-nuclear-program-strait.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 01:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与图恩和共和党不和，加剧了选举年的裂痕</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/trump-thune-republicans-election-year-rift.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统将他的情报提名人从确认听证会上剔除，并坚持结束阻挠，从而颠覆了多数党领袖的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/trump-thune-republicans-election-year-rift.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 01:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
