    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府将支付 7.65 亿美元取消另外 4 个风电项目</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/climate/trump-wind-farms-cancel-millions.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是内政部达成的第三笔此类协议，旨在向企业支付放弃海上涡轮机计划的费用，花费约 25 亿美元让企业放弃风电项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/climate/trump-wind-farms-cancel-millions.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
